{"tid":375281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GiGi 帶 囡 囡 返 錯 學","createTime":"2017-08-26T11:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T16:14:53.000Z","uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"85268fc1517ebbdb8ce419c344a7ff7b3bbec1a5","tid":375281,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:49:07.000Z","msg":"GiGi的兩歲囡囡Sofia已經返學前班，GiGi指已習慣早上7時多起床帶囡囡返學，不過昨日就發生返錯學的烏龍事件，她笑說：「今日同老公都擺咗個烏龍，一早帶囡囡返學，去到學校門口先發現水靜河飛，當時仲以為自己遲到，見到學校一個姨姨，問佢先知今日原來唔使返學，自己都覺得好好笑。」<br />\n<br />\n問Sofia不用上學有否好開心？GiGi謂：「其實我同老公都好想笑，但係唔想令Sofia覺得唔使返學係咁開心，所以我哋都忍住笑，同佢講話媽咪同爸爸搞錯咗，今日唔使返學，叫佢唔好失望，下星期再同佢返過。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170826/large/26ec1p7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170826%2Flarge%2F26ec1p7.jpg&h=07c47aa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3bab5c93a56776f19d7851fa9a6cd0f957d8702","tid":375281,"uid":5267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:51:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0682f60e9652ce021d6b2082f55c38efc073b9e","tid":375281,"uid":35749,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"馬英九看錶"},{"pid":"bde5dfdaed45063cc8f3ed7cd14c4dfeb0fcadb4","tid":375281,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西</blockquote><br />\n班"},{"pid":"58934090e4cad95c9ff0b72f2dac352f3e0def6a","tid":375281,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西</blockquote><br />\n班</blockquote><br />\n牙"},{"pid":"5a40b05d77d064e5a6869cbb69cb2d00e8b39593","tid":375281,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>西</blockquote><br />\n班</blockquote><br />\n牙</blockquote><br />\n籍"},{"pid":"f66769d6e66d739